extends sample.tpl.jade

block append vars
  - var page_type = 'interior'
  - var page_name = 'Hotel & Travel'
  - var page_description = 'Get information about the location of the conference and where to stay.'

block main
  section
    header.o-BodyChild__Inv.c-Hero(style="padding: 4rem 0 2rem; text-align: left;")
      h1(style="padding-top: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; padding-left: 1rem; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);").
        #[span.-d-n= conference_name + ' â€” ']Hotel &amp; Travel
    section.this-is-editable
      p: strong(style="color: red;") Editable section.
      h2 Hotel Information
      p.
        The reservation deadline for the hotel is
        #[time.c-Date(datetime="2016-01-14") Thursday, January 14, 2016] however rooms are
        selling out, so make sure you read this very long paragraph which probably
        no one will read because studies show that users of the web merely skim through
        the page to find the information most relavent to them in the fastest
        way possible.
      p(itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Place")
        span(itemprop="name") Sheraton Phoenix Downtown Hotel
        br
        span(itemprop="address" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/PostalAddress")
          span(itemprop="streetAddress") 340 North 3rd Street
          br
          span(itemprop="addressLocality") Phoenix, 
          abbr(itemprop="addressRegion" title="Arizona") AZ 
          span(itemprop="postalCode") 85004
        br
        a(href="" itemprop="url") https://sheraton.com/phoenix/
      h2 Transportation
      h3 Airport
      p(itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Place")
        span(itemprop="name") Phoenix Sky Harbor International Airport (PHX)
        br
        a(href="" itemprop="url") https://sheraton.com/phoenix/
        br
        a(href="" itemprop="telephone") 602-273-3300
      p.
        PHX is located #[del approximately]#[ins about] 6 miles from the Sheraton Phoenix Downtown Hotel
        and Phoenix Convention Center and no one will actually read this paragraph
        because they will probably just Google map it themselves.
      h3 Shuttle
      p.
        SuperShuttle Servidce costs approximately (again with the long words)
        $26 for a round-trip ride from the airport to the hotel then back to the airport,
        which is overly redundant for a web page.
      h3 Taxi Service
      p About $25 one-way from airport to hotel. See, that wasn&rsquo;t so bad, was it?
    div.o-GridFlex
      aside.o-GridFlex__Item.c-Callout
        h1 Questions?
        ul.o-ListBare
          li: a(href="") (800) 548-2723
          li: a(href="") +1 (703) 295-6300
          li: a(href="") registrations@asce.org
        p: ins This callout isn&rsquo;t necessary with the same information in the footer.
      aside.o-GridFlex__Item.c-Callout
        h1 Important Dates
        +important-date-block()
